snippet.title: Dry Drowning - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The gameplay trailer of Dry Drowning, the upcoming investigative visual novel developed by StudioV and published by VLG

DOWNLOAD THE DEMO NOW!
Steam: http://bit.ly/drydrowning-steam
GOG.com: http://bit.ly/drydrowningDEMO-GOG

If you enjoyed the DEMO, don't forget to wish list it! 
Want to leave us a feedback? Join our Discord server https://discord.gg/cn4h3Vc or our Steam Community Hub

NEXT on PlayStation4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch
